\c 27
\s Jotamu mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Jotamu waiva nemakore makumi maviri nemashanu paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nematanhatu paJerusarema. Uye zita ramai vake raiva Jerusha mukunda waZadhoki\x + 2 Madz. 15.32-35.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino wakaita zvakarurama pameso paJehovha, zvichienderana nezvese baba vake Uziya zvavakaita; koga haana kupinda mutembere yaJehovha. Uye vanhu vairamba vachiita zvakaora\x + 26.16.\x*.
\v 3 Iye wakavaka suwo rekumusoro reimba yaJehovha\x + 2 Madz. 15.35.\x*, nepachidziro cheshongwe\x + 33.14. Neh. 3.26,27. 11.21.\x* wakavaka zvizhinji.
\v 4 Wakavakawo maguta pamakomo aJudha, uye mumasango wakavaka dzinhare nedzishongwe\x + 17.12.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Iye wakarwawo namambo wevana vaAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x* ndokuvakunda. Vana vaAmoni ndokumupa mugore iroro matarenda* esirivha zana, nemakori* egorosi zvuru gumi, neebhari zvuru gumi. Vana vaAmoni vakadzosa izvi kwaari mugorewo rechipiri nerechitatu\x + 1 Madz. 4.22.\x*.
\v 6 Naizvozvo Jotamu wakazvisimbisa, nokuti wakagadzira nzira dzake pamberi paJehovha Mwari wake\x + 27.2.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino dzimwe dzenyaya dzaJotamu, nehondo dzake dzese, nenzira dzake, tarira, dzakanyorwa mubhuku remadzimambo aIsraeri naJudha\x + 2 Madz. 15.36.\x*.
\v 8 Waiva nemakore makumi maviri nemashanu paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nematanhatu paJerusarema\x + 27.1. 2 Madz. 15.33.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Jotamu wakarara nemadzibaba ake; ivo ndokumuviga muguta raDhavhidhi. Ahazi mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake\x + 2 Madz. 15.38.\x*.